Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.52,0:23:40.74,Title2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be10\fad(500,0)}畢業典禮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.37,0:00:28.58,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}晴れ渡る空は青く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.97,0:00:34.10,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}近づいてくる足音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.95,0:00:40.49,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}光りだした風に押されるように
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.58,0:00:45.57,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}ほら　出会ってしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.30,0:00:49.30,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}それぞれの夢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:52.41,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}それぞれの未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.51,0:00:58.02,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}負けないように走り
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.26,0:00:59.26,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}気づいたら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:04.48,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}ずっと一緒にいたんだ　誰よりも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.50,0:01:10.38,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}悩んで落ち込んで　泣いて笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:14.00,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}加速してく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.82,0:01:20.10,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}君に届け　空を駆けて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.13,0:01:25.50,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}真っ直ぐな思い　ギュっと抱きしめ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.53,0:01:31.84,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}きっと　生まれたての強さは胸に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.95,0:01:37.25,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}この気持ちが翼になり
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.39,0:01:44.04,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,500)}私は私を超えていく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.37,0:00:28.58,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}萬里晴空如此湛藍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.97,0:00:34.10,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}悄悄靠近著的腳步聲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.95,0:00:40.49,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}像是閃耀光芒的風推搡著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.58,0:00:45.57,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}你看  我們相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.30,0:00:49.30,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}各自的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:52.41,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}各自的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.51,0:00:58.02,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}為了不輸給任何人我們奔跑著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.26,0:00:59.26,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}等察覺時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:04.48,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}已經一直在一起了  比任何人都要久
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.50,0:01:10.38,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}煩惱著消沉著  哭泣  歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:14.00,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}然後加速
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.82,0:01:20.10,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}追逐著你  飛躍藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.13,0:01:25.50,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}緊緊擁抱那份執著的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.53,0:01:31.84,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}初生的力量聚集於這胸中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.95,0:01:37.25,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}我要將這份心情化為羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.39,0:01:44.04,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,500)}我要超越我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.86,0:22:24.81,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}ありふれた感情から  卒業もできてなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.97,0:22:27.79,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}眠れない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.98,0:22:32.97,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}突然の雨  ぬかるんだあの靴は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:41.62,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}瞬きする君の世界をじっと受け止めている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.91,0:22:48.34,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}君のリアル　僕の視線　どこか違うとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.53,0:22:55.29,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}あのくたびれたTシャツみたいにさせないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.41,0:22:57.12,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}Prime number
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.13,0:23:02.64,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}世界にどれひとつとして同じものがない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.81,0:23:09.18,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}ココロの空白を無理に埋めなくてもいいね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.31,0:23:16.61,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}たくさんの誰かの記憶に残されているよりも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.79,0:23:23.56,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,500)}屋根の上君だけの空になりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.86,0:22:24.81,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}不能從那俗不可耐的感情中畢業
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.97,0:22:27.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}無法入眠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.98,0:22:32.97,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}那雙鞋被突如其來的雨打濕而滿是泥濘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:41.62,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}靜靜地接受閃耀著的你的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.91,0:22:48.34,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}你的現實  我的視線  即使有所不同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.53,0:22:55.29,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}也不會讓它變成那穿舊了的T恤一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.41,0:22:57.12,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}Prime number
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.13,0:23:02.64,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}世界上沒有一個事物是相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.81,0:23:09.18,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}不用勉強去填補心中的空白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.31,0:23:16.61,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}比起在許多人心中留下記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.79,0:23:23.56,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be20\fad(200,200)}我更想成為屋頂上那片只屬於你的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.22,0:01:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.02,0:01:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽到了一種令人生厭的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:02.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變成這樣了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:04.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至能讓自己的心中的某物破碎一般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.13,0:02:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太不公平了  這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.74,0:02:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體發出哀嚎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.57,0:02:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管多麼想追上去  到最後還是無用功
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.97,0:02:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心靈像是被撕裂了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.50,0:02:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們明明已經努力到遍體鱗傷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.99,0:02:19.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正還是沒有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.47,0:02:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有將這份痛楚歸咎於別人才能保護自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.47,0:02:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都無能為力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.25,0:02:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我其實並不想說那種話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.24,0:02:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也是我嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.74,0:02:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學弟君  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:02:58.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學姐  你真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天可是畢業典禮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.00,0:03:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  讓我們打起精神出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的已經到了畢業典禮了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  美笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:11.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了飯  我和你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.52,0:03:15.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多該去叫真白起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.77,0:03:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然就沒時間吃早飯了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不行哦  學弟君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米飯可是力量的源泉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要大口大口地吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學弟君沒什麼精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.17,0:03:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我們才要振作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.70,0:03:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.56,0:03:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  神田君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…神田君沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.55,0:03:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山你才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:04:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能…沒事吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.95,0:04:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧了你  我好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.10,0:04:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不許想起我的哭腔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是大花臉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.61,0:04:10.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說女孩子不好看的神田君最討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:18.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以的話  真想忘記昨天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.87,0:04:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是想將昨天重新來過一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.39,0:04:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  忘掉剛剛的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  我得叫椎名起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.76,0:04:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椎名  我開門咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快起來  椎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椎名？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椎名！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.93,0:04:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.22,0:04:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.99,0:05:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椎名不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.99,0:05:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白她一早就出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:08.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拆除櫻花莊的原因是椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.21,0:05:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理由可想而知了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白…知道了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:16.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼老師沒有阻止她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可有好好問過她哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有和神田商量過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是剛來櫻花莊的真白的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.02,0:05:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時候大概也就是陷入混亂也不會去顧及你們的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧了你們  真白也變了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使在現在這種情況下這是件壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,GPS顯示她在學校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:48.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白大人  鎖定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走  學弟君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.42,0:05:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標  學校！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.59,0:05:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼連我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.92,0:06:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.98,0:06:12.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距真白大人還有30米
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.46,0:06:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,30米是哪個方向啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.13,0:06:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個位置是美術教室嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全力衝刺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.99,0:06:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是真白的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這畫是真白畫的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:42.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.93,0:06:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.24,0:06:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.58,0:06:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人都在…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:06:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這幅畫一定連名垂青史的畫家也畫不出
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這幅畫正是真白珍視櫻花莊的心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.82,0:07:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.11,0:07:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:20.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼只有你不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過正因如此我才明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻花莊由我來保護
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.18,0:07:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天真白是帶著什麼樣的心情說出那句話的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.17,0:07:38.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白打算聯名失敗就自己離開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.13,0:07:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從而來保護櫻花莊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣是不對的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.93,0:07:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這才不是我最喜歡的櫻花莊呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:47.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有這樣的道別
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就毫無意義了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:53.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田君…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼空太
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.38,0:07:56.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就該告訴她這點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.90,0:08:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  開始尋找真白大作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是真白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.32,0:08:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她不太可能一個人回英國
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她好像也沒一個人坐過電車
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只要去找附近她有可能去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託美笑學姐和仁學長在學校裏和學校附近找找
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.49,0:08:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,車站那邊  我去找
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢業典禮之前要回來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.07,0:08:30.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可已經打定主意要你們為我好好慶祝了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定會把真白帶回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:41.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼以防萬一  我就去櫻花莊那邊看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:50.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田君從商店街到車站那邊找
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便利店我來找
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到真白的話就通知我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:03.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.37,0:09:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的試鏡結果出來之後希望你能聽我說件事的約定…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.46,0:09:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我還記得
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:26.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得能遇到神田君真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.54,0:09:35.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能努力到現在都多虧了神田君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要看到神田君的臉就能打起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.38,0:09:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽到你的聲音  就能變得積極向上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.92,0:09:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等察覺的時候  我的目光就一直追隨著神田君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.39,0:09:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是衣服還是髮型
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要被你表揚  心情就變得好起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.38,0:09:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你說了很多話的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是這樣就真的能讓我努力下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你給我了很多努力下去的動力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這麼說  我也和你一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因為有青山在…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  所以啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請把這份真摯的感情也告訴真白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.82,0:10:24.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  青山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我能努力到今天的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.04,0:10:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為喜歡上了神田君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.40,0:10:40.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.63,0:10:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直來買這個的女孩有來過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.65,0:10:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用雙腳來找人太沒效率了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.28,0:10:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底  為什麼我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:56.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.18,0:11:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給寄宿女發封郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為櫻花莊拆除一事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椎名感到了自己的責任而出走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:06.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道她會去什麼地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.53,0:11:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啦  還真是開門見山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有出現國際通話的標誌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會感到疑惑是很正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:20.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  我在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.39,0:11:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是立體影像嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要摸一摸確認一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別…別靠過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對著擔心龍之介的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼是這種態度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.06,0:11:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要說這種要讓我感恩戴德的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.66,0:11:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有什麼要對我說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是有感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.24,0:11:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽不見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來  真是嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介想為仁和美笑做些什麼而發郵件給我的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介這種不坦率的樣子  我可是很喜歡的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.54,0:11:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別…別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找椎名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.30,0:11:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白的話  沒事的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.18,0:11:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼那麼肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要想過要擁有的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白就不會輕易放手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.61,0:12:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別看真白那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她可是世界上最任性  最頑固  最好勝的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.98,0:12:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是推銷報紙的  恕不接待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.31,0:12:26.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是熱情的歡迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明白是為什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然對孩子做這麼幼稚的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就是為了這件事來謝罪的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也覺得自己做了對不起神田君的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也沒有接到通知
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.28,0:12:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別的團隊竟然會來委託椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論有什麼理由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.54,0:12:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,採取措施才是你的工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:47.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是無言以對了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田的話他不在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.42,0:12:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏還是和原來一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種不聽自己不愛聽的話的性格和原來一模一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻花莊好像是要拆除了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.06,0:13:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛說完你就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼我能幫上忙的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有也不需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.73,0:13:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些小傢伙  會自己想辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那邊也沒有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.30,0:13:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我連大學都找過了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.01,0:13:21.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也去學校外面找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.89,0:13:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  難得為了讓我們不錯過畢業典禮才讓我們留在學校的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.09,0:13:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.63,0:13:32.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我們還有別的事要做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.63,0:13:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們倆還是一如既往的要好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.52,0:13:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有每次看到都是在一起出雙入對的前學生會長和皓皓那麼要好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.31,0:13:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們才沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.45,0:13:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我給你的情書
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是認真的話  就沒必要看了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皓皓的男朋友真帥氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.19,0:13:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那是當然的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.79,0:13:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就按原計劃交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:13:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真這麼想的話  就別把我扯進來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.96,0:14:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美笑  加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很期待皓皓的演奏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.44,0:14:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是神田家的小伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.86,0:14:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您看到過真白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.51,0:14:19.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,10分鐘之前看到她向車站方向那邊走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:20.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.39,0:14:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道怎麼回事  你要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青春就是爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.77,0:14:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一成不變的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我隱隱覺得有些無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有什麼新奇的事情發生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.42,0:14:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我便會將其歸咎於他人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:40.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當我在春天遇到了真白之後我便意識到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.76,0:14:45.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有心  就能瞬間改變世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.40,0:14:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  你想變成什麼顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.36,0:15:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.11,0:15:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.56,0:15:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:15.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一會會付錢的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.33,0:15:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你突然消失了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.59,0:15:31.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…如果我在的話櫻花莊就會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.87,0:15:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要緊的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.85,0:15:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.11,0:15:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天明明已經是畢業典禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.59,0:15:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筆記本卻沒有全部填滿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.90,0:15:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.14,0:15:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明需要很多簽名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.48,0:15:45.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不要緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.16,0:15:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.64,0:15:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可櫻花莊會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.86,0:15:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因為有我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.29,0:15:56.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還傷害了空太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被空太討厭…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:16:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:04.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要讓空太討厭了還硬要留在櫻花莊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的  不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.88,0:16:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了  給我聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.47,0:16:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  昨天我說的應該是我的真心話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.14,0:16:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠擁有一切想要的東西的你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是多麼的讓人羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想著為什麼總是你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.87,0:16:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.53,0:16:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至曾差點就開始討厭你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.79,0:16:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是並不只是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.98,0:16:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧了真白  我才找到了自己的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後我才努力去挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.71,0:17:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後因失敗而懊惱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而這一切的一切都是最棒的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是沒有遇到真白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就根本無從瞭解這種心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我喜歡教會了我一切的真白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.04,0:17:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜歡了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能討厭你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.94,0:17:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  不要走！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.87,0:17:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.83,0:17:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.44,0:18:00.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和空太在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:03.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想呆在櫻花莊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.78,0:18:06.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是要是我在的話櫻花莊就會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.30,0:18:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會給大家帶來麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.24,0:18:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會讓空太有著痛苦的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我受傷也不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:23.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,試鏡之後也讓七海忍耐了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想為了留在櫻花莊而去傷害別人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.55,0:18:35.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要把我的挫折扯到真白身上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.46,0:18:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,試鏡失敗全是我自己的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我個人的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.51,0:18:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這場經歷全是我自己的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.66,0:18:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不聽神田君的忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.67,0:18:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬要逞強  這都是我自己的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.55,0:18:54.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是隨便包攬責任   會讓我很困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.89,0:18:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山…不用說得這麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:18:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田君給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七海  正在生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看我像是不生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:06.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過啊  真白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為我擔心  我真的很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.66,0:19:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七海
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的非常感謝你  我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以啊  我可不允許真白擅自出走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.79,0:19:22.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七海
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.06,0:19:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是讓人頭疼的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.87,0:19:30.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是櫻花莊會消失都是因為我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.55,0:19:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不想走  卻不得不離開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.43,0:19:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是說了嗎  你不用離開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.89,0:19:40.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次碰到這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不知道該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.21,0:19:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸口好難受  一直很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.76,0:19:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.11,0:19:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.34,0:19:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田君有什麼想說的就說出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是在哭  也不會因此而壞掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.94,0:20:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對真白的淚水真沒抵抗力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.55,0:20:14.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.74,0:20:15.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.07,0:20:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一點都不瞭解櫻花莊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我瞭解的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.33,0:20:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你不瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.89,0:20:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所說的櫻花莊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.51,0:20:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並不是那棟破破爛爛的建築
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是有著美笑學姐  仁學長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.03,0:20:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青山  千尋老師  赤阪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.36,0:20:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有真白你在的才是櫻花莊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.54,0:20:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在才是櫻花莊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之我想說的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.87,0:20:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.48,0:20:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻花莊只有大家都在才是櫻花莊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家就是櫻花莊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:55.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:58.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會一直待在櫻花莊的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七海
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.83,0:21:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.12,0:21:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你說為我而高興
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.15,0:21:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.59,0:21:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很高興  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.09,0:21:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是當然的啦  因為我們是朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.72,0:21:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯  是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.53,0:21:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等  好疼啊真白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.96,0:21:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.02,0:21:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.83,0:21:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七海的話就不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.93,0:21:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.13,0:21:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾你們辦事真是抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.51,0:21:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過差不多該去學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.78,0:21:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗塔？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.64,0:21:36.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.29,0:21:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.43,0:21:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神田君  時間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.21,0:21:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢業典禮就要開始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.60,0:21:42.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.43,0:21:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.21,0:21:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:44.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍之介
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不用…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:47.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說啊  真白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.65,0:21:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.29,0:21:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我雖然還不知道自己想要變成什麼顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過今天倒是有了決定好的顏色
